Nice thing about this is that it is easy to setup, can [[chroot]] users, and works on [[OpenVZ]].

### Install and Start Proftpd
* sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 force-reload
* sudo apt-get update
* sudo apt-get install proftpd
* A new style of page should come up in the terminal. Follow the directions that fir your needs best
* sudo /etc/init.d/proftpd start
* ProFTPd is started from inetd/xinetd.

